node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Blurb™ in Los Angeles, California. May be an image of car and text that says 'Apple CEO confirms the tech giants are working on a driverless car (Apple Car) Sarah Unfriendly Black Techie @NerdyAndNatural It's the year 2032. You're driving on the highway to work in your apple car when you hear the news that the new Apple Car 2 is coming out. Suddenly the speed of your car goes from 95 to 25 mph. Chaos ensues.'.
Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I'm so sorry I'm late, the traffic was crazy... The traffic: STARBUCKS ORIVE THRU >> STARBUCIE'.
